Contain script to generate a "spacial" base dir from the default base dir
After you've run light_base.py you may wish to run

src/genbase/shrink_textures.sh base_light base_light
mkdir -p base_full
cd base
find . -type f -exec sh -c "[ -e ../base_light/{} ] || cp --parents {} ../base_full" \;
src/genbase/shrink_textures.sh base_full base_full
